platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Star Wars and toys go together like Wookiees and smugglers, but rarely so well as they do in these classic LEGO adventures. They’re all here—the most beloved characters, settings, and vehicles from the first six films, lovingly translated into plastic bricks for a wacky reenactment of George Lucas’s epic space odyssey. Thanks to instantly accessible controls and hours of action-packed gameplay, fans of all ages can jump in and relive their favorite scenes.
